title: Dishwasher Lower Spray Arm
description: Dishwasher Lower Spray Arm ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 30 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11770610 Manufacturer Part Number 5304507158 The spray arm rotates and sprays water to clean the dishes inside the dishwasher tub. This part works with the following brands: Frigidaire, White Westinghouse, Kelvinator, Gibson, Kenmore, Sears, Tappan, & Electrolux. Possible Repair Solution For: Not cleaning properly, unusual noises, leaking water.

installationInstructions.author: Melissa from W LAFAYETTE, IN
installationInstructions.title: The original lower spray arm has a blue circle sprayer that must have worn out and dislodged itself from the sprayer arm, it landed on the heating element and melted a bit!
installationInstructions.content: We easily removed the original sprayer arm, and clicked the new sprayer arm right into place. I know *very little* about appliances/repairs, etc but this was so easy and an affordable repair for our dishwasher.
